        Instantiator with a pre-existing amazonS3Client, this is used to help with re-use.
        Parameters:
        amazonS3Client - If you have an existing amazonS3Client, it wont' bother to create another one
        s3WriterConfiguration - Configuration of the write paths and instructions are still required.
